only for 12 weeks.

315
00:13:56,840 --> 00:14:00,440
I see myself probably,
maybe, like,

316
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:02,840
a month.

317
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:04,640
That's...

318
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:08,040
I don't see myself
taking longer than that.

319
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:13,000
I don't know how I could
take longer than that.

320
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:18,760
So...
probably like a month.

321
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:21,160
That is a woman

322
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:23,160
who deserves real gratitude

323
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:26,160
in the form of a Tampa Bay
Rays flower pot,

324
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:28,840
just to help her
and the baby.

325
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:31,400
And that's if your pregnancy
goes according to plan.

326
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:34,200
If a baby is born prematurely,
parents can be forced

327
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:36,440
to make some truly
heart-wrenching choices,

328
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:39,240
like Selena Allen, whose baby
was six weeks premature

329
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,960
and who knew
that she could only afford

330
00:14:41,040 --> 00:14:43,240
to take four weeks off
in total.

331
