00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:51,560
when he was home with us.

334
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:54,200
I gave birth
on a Wednesday.

335
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:57,200
And on Monday,
I went back to work.

336
00:14:57,280 --> 00:15:00,680
It was like a piece of me
got left in that hospital,

337
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:03,120
and now I had to pretend
that I'm okay.

338
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:06,040
Okay, that's terrible.

339
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:07,720
Although, I will say,

340
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,960
you have definitely got
everyone's bullshit

