396
00:17:26,600 --> 00:17:29,840
"That's all I'm saying.
No to wolves !

397
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:31,840
"No to the wolves !

398
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:34,040
Think about the wolves !"

