00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:41,040
and a 2012 survey
found few work sites

401
00:17:41,120 --> 00:17:43,680
reported negative effects
of complying with the law.

402
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:45,680
So we thought
the bill would kill us,

403
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:48,000
but instead we just got used
to having it around,

404
00:17:48,080 --> 00:17:51,000
like an irregular mole
or a new step-dad.

405
00:17:51,080 --> 00:17:54,120
"I don't know why
I was so afraid of you, Gene.

406
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:56,160
You were fine."

407
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:58,280
Now, some people might argue,

408
00:17:58,360 --> 00:18:00,640
"But that was unpaid leave.

409
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:03,920
Paid leave is too onerous."
But is it ?

410
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,920
Because back in 2002,
California passed a plan

411
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:09,360
