of partially-paid leave

412
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:11,400
funded through
a small payroll tax.

413
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:13,600
Essentially,
it was an insurance plan

414
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:16,000
that would cost employers
little to nothing.

415
00:18:16,080 --> 00:18:18,360
But all the same
fear-mongering took place,

416
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:20,440
and in the end,
this happened.

417
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:23,040
More than 90%
of the companies there

418
00:18:23,120 --> 00:18:26,920
reported either positive
or, at worst, neutral effect.

419
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:29,080
Businesses seemed
to just make it work.

420
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:32,320
And the polling data we have
when we survey them,

421
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:35,040
most of them say
it's just not a big deal.

