00:19:57,280 --> 00:19:59,400
and every other lawmaker
you just saw

455
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:01,400
voted against that bill.

456
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:03,600
And you can't
have it both ways.

457
00:20:03,680 --> 00:20:06,200
You can't go on and on about how much
you love mothers

458
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:08,200
and then fail
to support legislation

459
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:10,200
that makes life
easier for them.

460
00:20:10,280 --> 00:20:12,040
In fact, until we...

461
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:16,360
Until we as a country
do something to address this,

462
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:18,240
this should be
the only message

463
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:20,560
that we're allowed to send
on Mother's Day.

464
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:21,960
Mothers.

465
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:24,280
We owe everything
to them.

466
00:20:24,360 --> 00:20:26,920
They gave birth to us.
They nurtured us.

467
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,920
They made us who we are.

468
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:32,600
And this Mother's Day,
we have just one thing to say

469
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:34,800
to all the mothers out there.

470
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:36,920
Get the fuck back to work.

471
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:39,280
Seriously,
get back to work now.

472
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:41,640
