00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:52,240
We'd do anything
for our moms,

477
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:53,920
up to, but not including,

478
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,920
paying them to stay home
for a while

479
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:58,040
after pushing a human being
