00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:46,080
taking care of everyone.

500
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:49,920
Because remember, not only
can you balance work and family,

501
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:51,560
you have to.

502
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:53,560
And that's why
this Mother's Day,

503
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:55,560
we know you'll be grateful,
moms,

504
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:57,360
because you understand
that even though

505
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:59,840
183 other countries
do more for you,

