to the public,

566
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:56,080
a parrot holding
an olive branch named Shaloum-chan.

567
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:59,720
I believe some Japanese will see Israel
like this character.

568
00:24:59,800 --> 00:25:04,200
Look, people see Israel
a lot of different ways.

569
00:25:04,280 --> 00:25:06,400
But I don't think
there is anyone on Earth

570
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:08,760
that sees it
as that character.

571
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:10,760
But that just proves
the power

572
00:25:10,840 --> 00:25:13,320
mascots have to reach out
and engage people.

573
00:25:13,400 --> 00:25:16,280
Although, not all
are instantaneously lovable.

574
00:25:16,360 --> 00:25:19,080
For example,
the prefecture of Nara

575
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:20,920
